## `test_bench_write_4k(mount)`
<!-- checksum: placeholder-bench-3 -->
<!-- trace: skipped -->
<!-- trace_skip_reason: runtime measurement -->

### Postconditions

```python
path = mount / "f"
path.touch()

# Sustained 4 KiB writes in-place.
data = b"x" * 4096
with open(path, "wb") as f:
    def write_one():
        f.seek(0)
        f.write(data)
    per_op = _measure(write_one, iterations=500)
assert per_op < 5e-3, f"4K write too slow: {per_op * 1e6:.1f} us/op"
```

