## `test_bench_ripgrep_over_tree(mount)`
<!-- checksum: placeholder-bench-8 -->
<!-- trace: skipped -->
<!-- trace_skip_reason: runtime measurement + external tool -->

### Postconditions

```python
if not shutil.which("rg"):
    pytest.skip("ripgrep not installed")

# Seed ~1000 small files.
for i in range(1000):
    (mount / f"f{i:04d}.txt").write_text(f"content_{i}\n" * 10)

start = time.perf_counter()
subprocess.run(["rg", "-r", "content_500", str(mount)],
               capture_output=True)   # no check= — rg exits 1 on no match
elapsed = time.perf_counter() - start
assert elapsed < 3.0, f"ripgrep over 1000 files: {elapsed:.2f}s"
```

